<p xml:id="t2838.p1" n="1-2" corresp="c2838.1">…… offerings ……, he brought (?) them into <w type="TN">E-kur</w>.</p>
<p xml:id="t2838.p2" n="3-8" corresp="c2838.3">In the <w type="TN">E-kur</w>, the house of <w type="DN">Enlil</w>, <w type="RN"><w type="DN">Samsu</w>-ilūna</w>, the mighty king 
<addSpan to="t2838.v1"/>whose …… awesomeness covers all people
<anchor xml:id="t2838.v1"/>
<addSpan to="t2838.v2"/><note xml:id="t2838.n1" target="t2838.v1">an Akkadian gloss has:</note> whose splendour covers all people
<anchor xml:id="t2838.v2"/>
<addSpan to="t2838.v3"/><gap extent="1 line unclear"/>
<anchor xml:id="t2838.v3"/>
<addSpan to="t2838.v4"/><note xml:id="t2838.n2" target="t2838.v3">an Akkadian gloss has:</note> reach ……
<anchor xml:id="t2838.v4"/>
<gap extent="3 lines fragmentary"/></p>
